samp_store_method_additional: Stored in a 1 L brown Nalgene bottle
samp_mat_process: Water samples were collected from the niskin into 1 L bottles then filtered through a 0.22 micron sterivex filter using a peristaltic pump with tubing attached to the outlet end of the sterivex.
prep_method_additional: 2 mL of 96% molecular grade ethanol used for preservation
nucl_acid_ext_kit: Qiagen DNeasy Blood and Tissue Kit
nucl_acid_ext_modify: Modified for sterivex with QiaVac 24 Plus, reagent volume altered
concentration_method: Qubit Fluorometer v.4 dsDNA high sensitivity kit
nucl_acid_ext_method_additional: Extractions completed in a Biosafety Cabinet for sterility purposes.
DepthInMeters_method: maximumDepthInMeters was calculated using the pressure and the decimalLatitude to get the depth. Python's GSW conversion library was used, using the z_from_p function. minimumDepthInMeters was calculated by subtracting 1 m from the output maximumDepthInMeters to account for the size of the Niskin bottle.
tot_depth_water_col_method: Looked up in the GEBCO 2024 bathymetric dataset using the decimalLatitude and decimalLongitude coordinates.
measurements_from: Environmental metadata measurements reported for this sample are taken from a mix of the CTD data file and bottle file. wind_direction, wind_speed, turbidity, salinity, chlorophyll, and temp are from the bottle file. diss_oxygen, nitrate, nitrite, phosphate, percent_oxygen_sat, density, and PAR are from the CTD data file. Pressure is primarily recorded from the bottle file, but samples E1148.DY2206, E1149.DY2206, E1158.DY2206, D1159.DY2206, and E1160.DY2206 have pressure recorded from the CTD file. Altitude, maximumDepthInMeters, minimumDepthInMeters, and tot_depth_water_col were calculated using the methods described in the field's corresponding method field. If not specified in the corresponding method field, then the field was measured.
altitude_method: Calculated by subtracting the maximumDepthInMeters from the tot_depth_water_col.

measurements_from: Environmental metadata measurements reported for this sample are taken from a mix of the CTD data file and bottle file. wind_direction, wind_speed, turbidity, salinity, chlorophyll, and temp are from the bottle file. diss_oxygen, nitrate, nitrite, phosphate, percent_oxygen_sat, density, and PAR are from the CTD data file. Pressure is primarily recorded from the bottle file, but samples E1148.DY2206, E1149.DY2206, E1158.DY2206, D1159.DY2206, and E1160.DY2206 have pressure recorded from the CTD file. Altitude, maximumDepthInMeters, minimumDepthInMeters, and tot_depth_water_col were calculated using the methods described in the field's corresponding method field. If not specified in the corresponding method field, then the field was measured.
